I usually just use |slice for this.

```{% for row in hubdb_table_rows(XXXXXX)|slice(10, '') %}
  &lt;div class="row-fluid"&gt;
    {% for item in row %}
      {% if item %}
        &lt;div class="row-item"&gt;
          {{ item }}
        &lt;/div&gt;
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  &lt;/div&gt;
{% endfor %}```
